{"tid":1693852,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"真兇係奧里亞　趕走孫興民另有原因","createTime":"2019-11-05T00:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T03:55:17.000Z","uid":8929,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c1928d2cac36eae905c03b5bdbc62a57b20b0e1e","tid":1693852,"uid":8929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T00:10:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20191104/mobile/bkn-20191104120127281-1104_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20191104%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191104120127281-1104_00882_001.html&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcatywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=957ebef2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20191104/mobile/bkn-20191104120127281-1104_00882_001.html</a><br />\n熱刺前鋒孫興民從後攔截安祖高美斯，被球證紅牌趕出場，但其實令到安祖高美斯斷腳嘅人係奧里亞，但呢位後衞連黃牌都冇，惹起爭議。<br />\n<br />\n當時老孫從後踢到安祖高美斯，後者失平衡同奧利亞撞埋一堆，奧利亞雙腳夾住高美斯隻右腳，就咁夾斷咗佢嘅足踝，嚴格嚟講，令到高美斯斷腳嘅真兇其實係奧里亞。<br />\n<br />\n電光火石之間，孫興民可能誤以為自己踢斷高美斯隻腳，情緒完全崩潰。呢位南韓國腳嘅犯規，畀黃牌比較合理，球證原本都係準備出示黃牌，但睇完高美斯傷勢後，改判紅牌，問題係根本唔係老孫踢斷佢隻腳。<br />\n<br />\n有分析認為球證其實係想保護孫興民，因為佢當時嘅情緒已經無法繼續比賽，而且留喺場上，亦可能遭對手報復，所以順勢趕佢出場。事實上，熱刺領隊普捷天奴之後亦將真兇奧利亞換走，以免事件影響佢精神集中力而誤事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牙son<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7310e2ebcce26037febc1efc6a6f795480588d37","tid":1693852,"uid":64464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:14:15.000Z","msg":"牙申矛做錯刀"},{"pid":"c2f2695979d3617d973663ce8342cad333ea4c2e","tid":1693852,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:15:53.000Z","msg":"連攞紅牌都係有球證幫住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53812b168c02bf6f88262e77f269bd7419a8990d","tid":1693852,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685f77f90e460ab53b3a6bd3f579d220668240fa","tid":1693852,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:43:37.000Z","msg":"FIFA20 有咩方法可以整到自己隻右閘斷腳呢<br />\n利伸 ：用熱刺"},{"pid":"55f7540f8b98e1dd9b6cd1b42d6c99b98ce2ff6b","tid":1693852,"uid":6658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}